Hi I'd like access to the api token

Sure, I can help you with that! To fetch your API Access Token, please log in to the Newsbreak Admanager Platform. Then click on Tools - Resources - API Access Tokens. Here you can click 'Generate token' to create your own API access token. Please remember that this token is tied to your user ID and should not be shared with anyone else. For more detailed instructions, you can refer to this article: [API Integration Guide](https://help.newsbreak.com/hc/en-us/articles/27680147056397-API-Integration-Guide).
